casebody.data:
MISSOURI, ex rel. KCP & L GREATER MISSOURI OPERATIONS COMPANY, petitioner,
v.
MISSOURI PUBLIC SERVICE COMMISSION, et al. No. 13-787. Supreme Court of the United States June 30, 2014. Case below, 408 S.W.3d 153 . Motion of Edison Electric Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Missouri, Western District denied.
